               <text ID="inv-39bcb6ef-fbaf-4860-809e-9c5f29535662">
                  <paragraph>
                     <br/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Megestrol acetate tablets, 40 mg, are white, round, flat-faced, beveled-edged, bisected, debossed with “Par 290” on one side. They are supplied in <br/>
                  </paragraph>
